{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dicey Chess</strong> is a chess game in which the throw of the die decides how far you can move, adding a layer of unpredictability to every move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892190/extras/roll.gif?t=1735573077\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Highly Customizable</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Die Ranges</strong>: Make the pawn be able to walk between 1 and 3 or even 1 and 7 cells by modifying its die.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Piece Types</strong>: Randomize the types of pieces you will be playing with. You could end up with 10 rooks or even 5 kings requiring your enemy to capture all of them to win.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Piece Movements</strong>: Randomize the way your pieces can move. Have the pawn move like a knight or the rook like a bishop. Even combinations are possible.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Turn Timer</strong>: Set your own pace with customizable turn timers. Or if you are feeling lucky you can also randomize it!</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Play Anywhere</strong>: Challenge friends online or over a local network, or go up  against a powerful Bot.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Small but Mighty","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2892190/b79fdf31d5a5303b7ccdcb580f5c47d0611370f2.jpg"},{"name":"Immovable Ruler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2892190/1ca5648dbae6009df0ba6e63a8014d78dd514468.jpg"},{"name":"Checkmate Express","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2892190/1ff8e80bde0af4a7707